Paper: hep-th/9911223

Date: 1999-11-28

Title: Anomaly inflow and RR anomalous couplings

Authors: Claudio A. Scrucca and Marco Serone

Comments: 9 pages, LaTex, Talk given by C.A. Scrucca at TMR meeting "Quantum

aspects of gauge theories, supersymmetry and unification", ENS, Paris, 1-7September 1999Journal-ref: PRHEP tmr99 (1999) 047

We review the anomaly inflow mechanism on D-branes and O-planes. Inparticular, we compute the one-loop world-volume anomalies and derive the RRanomalous couplings required for their cancellation.